Sun Jun 22 Dominique Michel
  * Applied the gentoo POSIX fix for the env variables.
  * Changed the fvwm exec name into bin/fbwm-crystal in order to use the new and now old fvwm2 exec name: fvwm
  * Backported some of the chamges made into the svn repository:
    * All the ascii files are encoded using UTF-8.
    * Changed the fvwm exec name into bin/fbwm-crystal in order to use the new and now old fvwm2 exec name: fvwm
  * Taged 3.0.6
  
